Title : Bruvik
Text : '''Bruvik''' may refer to:

==Places==
*[[Bruvik, Hordaland]], a village in Osterøy municipality, Hordaland county, Norway
*[[Bruvik (municipality)]], a former municipality in Hordaland county, Norway
*[[Bruvik Church]], a church in Osterøy municipality, Hordaland county, Norway

==People with the surname==
*[[Olav Bruvik]] (1913–1962), Norwegian trade unionist and politician for the Labour Party
*[[Trygve Bruvik]] (born 1952), Norwegian engineer and businessman

